.TH PRODBOX 1
.SH NAME
prodbox \- Home Kubernetes operator
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B prodbox
[GLOBAL OPTIONS] COMMAND
.SH DESCRIPTION
Typed command registry for the supported prodbox command surface.
.SH COMMAND GROUPS
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
\fBaws\fR
AWS IAM and quota management
.TP
\fBcharts\fR
Bespoke Helm chart lifecycle
.TP
\fBcheck-code\fR
Run policy, lint, and type checks
.TP
\fBcommands\fR
Render the command registry
.TP
\fBconfig\fR
Configuration management
.TP
\fBdns\fR
Route 53 inspection
.TP
\fBdocs\fR
Generated-documentation maintenance
.TP
\fBgateway\fR
Gateway daemon operations
.TP
\fBhelp\fR
Render help for a command path
.TP
\fBhost\fR
Host prerequisite checks
.TP
\fBk8s\fR
Kubernetes helpers
.TP
\fBlint\fR
Doctrine lint surfaces
.TP
\fBpulumi\fR
AWS validation stack lifecycle
.TP
\fBrke2\fR
Local cluster lifecycle
.TP
\fBtest\fR
Named test suites
.TP
\fBtla-check\fR
Run TLA+ checks
.TP
\fBusers\fR
Operator-invited user management
.TP
\fBworkload\fR
Internal public workload runtime
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
\fBprodbox config validate\fR
Validate the repository Dhall config.
.TP
\fBprodbox test all\fR
Run the full test surface.
